WEBVTT

00:23.569 --> 00:25.369
Subtitles by explosiveskull

00:27.680 --> 00:29.659
You know that
feeling you get when you look down

00:29.661 --> 00:32.293
at the pool and you start to
inch your way in.

00:32.692 --> 00:36.027
Waiting because you don't want
to feel the water.

00:36.029 --> 00:38.262
My mom used to tell us you're
supposed to feel stuff.

00:38.264 --> 00:40.998
So don't cheat yourself out of a
great moment.

00:41.000 --> 00:44.102
You can spend you whole life
waiting with your toes in the water.

00:44.105 --> 00:45.872
Or you could just dive in.

00:52.445 --> 00:55.179
She could always
make an adventure out of anything

00:55.181 --> 00:57.683
And her voice echoes to us
everyday.

00:59.186 --> 01:00.452
That's my brother,

01:00.454 --> 01:02.287
Our parents promised us that on
their

01:02.289 --> 01:04.456
fifteenth wedding anniversary
they'd take us

01:04.458 --> 01:07.025
to the island where they got
married.

01:07.027 --> 01:08.793
We knew the island would be fun,

01:08.795 --> 01:10.861
but we never knew we'd meet a
special friend

01:10.863 --> 01:13.165
that would change our lives
forever.

01:15.000 --> 01:16.100
Our buddy Echo!

01:18.872 --> 01:20.038
The Dolphin.

03:11.815 --> 03:14.351
Bro bro bro, did you see that
cannonball?!

03:15.052 --> 03:18.989
It's spring break! Mom would
have wanted you to have fun.

03:22.892 --> 03:24.328
Do you want to jump in?

03:28.065 --> 03:30.231
Fine, we won't go on the deep
side.

03:30.233 --> 03:31.969
It's the same difference.

03:32.902 --> 03:33.904
Luke!

03:34.270 --> 03:35.838
It's been years

03:36.040 --> 03:38.475
Please don't let another summer
go by.

03:38.975 --> 03:40.541
You don't have to be afraid!

03:40.543 --> 03:41.545
I'm not afraid.

03:43.179 --> 03:45.915
- It's just I don't know what the big deal is anywa...
- Yeah swimming is fun but...

03:46.884 --> 03:48.518
with... without you

03:49.117 --> 03:50.119
it's not.

03:52.088 --> 03:53.054
Hey Skylar!

03:53.056 --> 03:54.826
- Let's go to practice!
- Come on!

03:55.624 --> 03:56.827
Got to go bro.

03:57.125 --> 03:58.327
You're missing out.

03:59.528 --> 04:00.797
Hey Sky!

04:01.164 --> 04:03.163
Why doesn't your brother swim
anymore?

04:03.165 --> 04:06.067
Yeah, is there something
wrong with him or what?

04:06.069 --> 04:07.501
Is he ever going to come back?

04:07.503 --> 04:09.907
He will when he's ready!

04:16.612 --> 04:17.846
Hunter!

04:18.380 --> 04:19.849
Hey Clint!

04:20.482 --> 04:23.151
Hey Clint! Hey man!

04:24.253 --> 04:25.653
- Hey!
- Hey what's up?

04:25.655 --> 04:28.321
Alright guys get on the
set let's go. Hey coach!

04:28.323 --> 04:29.924
Hey, how's it going?

04:29.926 --> 04:32.061
- Been alright.
- Good to see you.

04:32.426 --> 04:34.294
Taking it one day at a time.

04:34.296 --> 04:38.302
- I think about y'all a lot.
- I appreciate it, yeah.

04:39.267 --> 04:41.467
I came to check see about, uh,
taking

04:41.469 --> 04:43.302
Skylar and Luke on vacation.

04:43.304 --> 04:45.371
So I want to get a routine
for her while we're out there.

04:45.373 --> 04:46.609
I'm good with that.

04:47.376 --> 04:49.879
- Twice a day though.
- Twice a day!?

04:50.212 --> 04:52.445
- That means I gotta get up twice a day.
- Hey dad!

04:52.447 --> 04:53.583
Hey baby!

04:53.981 --> 04:55.915
Do they have pizza on Taino
island?

04:55.917 --> 04:58.652
Nope we have to do our own hunting.
You ready to go hunting?

04:58.654 --> 04:59.455
No.

05:00.154 --> 05:02.353
Alright get back in the pool.

05:02.355 --> 05:04.056
Hey! Uh uh!

05:04.058 --> 05:05.928
Hey! Whoa! Water bug!

05:07.162 --> 05:08.164
No cannonballs!

05:09.464 --> 05:12.100
- I'm a cannonball that's what I do!
- Taino Island...

05:13.135 --> 05:14.534
Isn't that where y'all married?

05:14.536 --> 05:16.301
- Yeah.
- Hey dad watch this!

05:16.303 --> 05:17.905
Hey no! Uh uh! Sky!

05:18.340 --> 05:20.508
No running there dad!

06:55.300 --> 06:56.302
Ah.

06:57.135 --> 06:58.136
Oh, cap'n...

06:58.570 --> 06:59.736
Nice and heavy.

06:59.738 --> 07:01.003
Good catch.

07:01.005 --> 07:03.608
You know I don't like when you
say that man you can jinx us!

07:04.209 --> 07:06.478
Alright, let me go cut up
this bait.

07:09.313 --> 07:10.347
Oh no.

07:10.349 --> 07:11.351
- Cap'n.
- What?

07:12.050 --> 07:13.519
We got a problem.

07:15.421 --> 07:17.123
- Out of bait.
- Come on, Moe, man!

07:18.223 --> 07:21.424
Boy what you been doing when I
be getting the boat prepped eh?

07:21.426 --> 07:24.492
Cap man, I gotta get my beauty
rest you know gotta sleep.

07:24.495 --> 07:25.594
All we need to do...

07:25.596 --> 07:27.433
Just go back, head back to the
dock.

07:27.632 --> 07:30.035
Get some bait, it ain't that
hard. Whoa!

07:31.603 --> 07:33.072
Cap'n, what is that?

07:33.504 --> 07:35.472
Little something I made at home.

07:35.474 --> 07:36.476
Special.

07:36.773 --> 07:37.775
Uh!

07:38.341 --> 07:39.343
What?!

07:40.511 --> 07:44.017
- Cutting out the middle man.
- By blowing up the boat?

07:47.785 --> 07:51.124
Oh lord am I going crazy,
gonna blow us all up to sky high.

08:02.533 --> 08:03.535
This is heaven!

08:04.735 --> 08:05.737
Wooo!

08:06.304 --> 08:07.304
Yes it is.

08:11.109 --> 08:13.875
Alright guys, I gotta go find
the boat rental company, OK?

08:13.877 --> 08:15.609
So you guys can look around a
little bit.

08:15.611 --> 08:16.710
But don't go far.

08:16.712 --> 08:18.315
Stay where I can see you ok?

08:18.549 --> 08:20.181
- Alright?
- Yeah, yeah, yeah, cool.

08:20.183 --> 08:21.653
Alright I'll be right over here.

08:22.284 --> 08:23.655
We got this.

08:24.155 --> 08:27.159
- Five minutes OK.
- Yes! Now, let's go shopping.

08:56.486 --> 08:59.255
Whoa! Watch yourself little man.

09:09.597 --> 09:11.767
<i>You don't have to be afraid.</i>

09:40.196 --> 09:42.764
<i>Yeah swimming is fun but...</i>

09:43.365 --> 09:45.301
<i>Without you it's not.</i>

10:36.316 --> 10:37.852
Hey buddy. Come here.

10:53.767 --> 10:54.768
Hi sweetie.

10:55.903 --> 10:58.772
- Shopping alone today?
- Oh no my father sent me to...

10:59.305 --> 11:01.209
- wait with my brother.
- Oh.

11:01.874 --> 11:05.510
- He's a bit of a wanderer eh?
- Whoops I gotta go!

11:19.493 --> 11:20.493
Hey buddy.

11:21.862 --> 11:23.497
Come here, come closer.

11:24.531 --> 11:25.766
Oh. My. Gosh!

11:27.566 --> 11:29.034
It's a dolphin.

11:29.036 --> 11:30.603
Aw, so cute!

11:31.470 --> 11:33.239
Come here. Come here! Come here!

11:33.640 --> 11:35.276
Where did he come from?

11:35.875 --> 11:38.679
I don't know
I guess he found us.

11:39.478 --> 11:42.348
- I think he wants to play fetch.
- I doubt that.

11:45.751 --> 11:47.621
Dude it's not a dog.

11:47.887 --> 11:49.823
So let's teach him!

11:53.659 --> 11:56.763
OK, so I take it from
you and then I throw it!

11:58.431 --> 11:59.432
Ready?

12:04.337 --> 12:05.505
Now you go get it.

12:06.604 --> 12:07.606
Grab it!

12:10.041 --> 12:12.878
Come on dogs and people do this
all of the time.

12:13.078 --> 12:14.580
It's fun just try it.

12:19.418 --> 12:21.383
Whoa what?

12:21.385 --> 12:23.890
- I call next!
- He's got it, he's doing it.

12:26.390 --> 12:28.560
Come here, come here.
This is so cool!

12:29.126 --> 12:31.994
Oh my gosh can we take him home.
He can even fit in our pool!

12:31.996 --> 12:34.033
- Woo-Hoo!
- Maybe even our bath tub.

12:34.698 --> 12:38.667
- Ah yes! Come on, come on.
- I want to take him home!

12:38.669 --> 12:40.004
You need to come with
us.

12:40.006 --> 12:42.604
- Ah that is awesome!
- You want to come with us?

12:42.606 --> 12:44.677
You want to come with us?

12:48.078 --> 12:50.646
- Yeah let's go show dad!
- Want to come with us?

12:50.648 --> 12:53.619
- Yeah follow us!
- Let's go show dad!

13:02.793 --> 13:03.795
Wow!

13:08.766 --> 13:10.600
Hello down there!

13:15.172 --> 13:17.638
- Can we just move here?
- It's gorgeous isn't it?

13:17.640 --> 13:18.642
Awesome!

13:19.144 --> 13:20.610
Go find you rooms!

13:22.111 --> 13:23.714
Found my room!

13:26.582 --> 13:27.818
Punch it!

13:29.053 --> 13:32.123
No, not yet we're not
in open water yet sweetie!

13:35.057 --> 13:36.958
Along with everything else the
first

13:36.960 --> 13:40.732
thing you put on is a life vest
when you get in a boat.

13:41.498 --> 13:43.131
These decks are slippery on a
boat.

13:43.133 --> 13:44.598
You slip and hit your head and
go over.

13:44.600 --> 13:48.170
I don't care how strong a swimmer
you are you're not going to do well.

13:48.172 --> 13:49.469
Check!

13:49.472 --> 13:51.374
What do we do next?

13:52.709 --> 13:53.711
Luke!

13:57.514 --> 13:58.515
Luke?

13:58.915 --> 13:59.916
Gas!

14:00.517 --> 14:01.619
Gas is not bad.

14:03.118 --> 14:05.752
Gotta make sure the boat's not
taking on water first.

14:05.754 --> 14:07.824
Looks like it's floating to me.

14:08.056 --> 14:09.857
Yeah she's floating sweetie.

14:09.859 --> 14:11.162
But there's a plug in the back.

14:11.594 --> 14:13.693
Gotta make sure it's in all the
way.

14:13.695 --> 14:14.965
Then you check fuel.

14:18.000 --> 14:20.870
Then last, we check for flares
and paddles.

14:22.003 --> 14:23.005
Check!

14:23.772 --> 14:25.475
Now can we go?

14:25.907 --> 14:28.177
Not yet sweetie we need open
water.

14:32.849 --> 14:35.484
Alright we got open water,
everybody holding on?

14:35.685 --> 14:36.550
Sit down!

14:36.552 --> 14:38.618
- Yes sir!
- Yup I'm good!

14:38.620 --> 14:40.621
Alright Sky,
you can go ahead and say it now.

14:40.623 --> 14:41.624
Punch it!

14:54.603 --> 14:55.603
Whoa!

14:56.738 --> 14:57.739
Whoa!

14:59.241 --> 15:00.543
That boy is fast!

15:09.117 --> 15:12.184
Just in time to do
absolutely nothing thank you!

15:12.186 --> 15:14.821
- I was working...
- Working lion research.

15:14.823 --> 15:17.827
- Lion, lion research. All the lions of the ocean.
- Lion research.

15:18.593 --> 15:20.628
Think you'll get this
guy here.

15:21.729 --> 15:23.598
Uh, ok so here's the deal

15:23.832 --> 15:25.998
pretty sure this dude is like a
trained MMA fighter,

15:26.000 --> 15:27.001
so let's be chill.

15:27.968 --> 15:29.568
Uh ok tough
guys we're all going.

15:29.570 --> 15:30.940
Hey brother what's up?

15:31.639 --> 15:34.139
- How you doing?
- Hey man you TUCC'd?

15:34.141 --> 15:35.543
Excuse me?

15:35.910 --> 15:36.777
We're T-U-C-C.

15:36.779 --> 15:38.943
Taino underwater clean up
committee.

15:38.945 --> 15:39.813
Oh?

15:39.815 --> 15:41.246
Yeah we're giving out
complimentary

15:41.248 --> 15:42.748
mugs so we can have a litter
free island.

15:42.750 --> 15:44.720
The metal is so much better for
the island.

15:44.952 --> 15:47.119
We find those cups all
over the beach underwater,

15:47.121 --> 15:49.787
- that we clean up so...
- I appreciate it thank y'all.

15:49.789 --> 15:51.189
Anything to keep the beaches
clean.

15:51.191 --> 15:52.558
Thank you.

15:52.560 --> 15:54.692
But, uh, I don't remember
this last time I was out here.

15:54.694 --> 15:55.827
Oh you've been here before?

15:55.829 --> 15:57.162
Yeah, it's been a while
honeymoon.

15:57.164 --> 15:58.996
Would your wife like one too?

15:58.998 --> 16:01.667
It's just me and the kids this
time.

16:01.669 --> 16:04.336
Well, uh, hey you're doing it wrong
if you only chill at this resort.

16:04.338 --> 16:07.972
- I mean I know it's cool but...
- You gotta venture out see the real Taino!

16:07.974 --> 16:09.807
We would love too, the
resort doesn't tell

16:09.809 --> 16:11.710
you about any of the
external life going on.

16:11.712 --> 16:13.979
They want to keep you here
drinking the ten dollar lemonades.

16:13.981 --> 16:14.982
Ten dollars!

16:15.916 --> 16:17.715
I'm telling you man, you got
ripped off.

16:18.986 --> 16:20.685
I believe you.

16:20.687 --> 16:22.686
- Hey guys, see you at Outriggers tonight?
- Oh yeah!

16:22.688 --> 16:24.321
- Yeah man Outriggers for sure.
- Of course!

16:24.323 --> 16:27.325
Outriggers, you would get that
much cheaper and much better.

16:27.327 --> 16:29.293
It has the best switcha on the
island man.

16:29.295 --> 16:30.394
Switcha? What's that?

16:30.396 --> 16:32.864
Lemonade man, that's what we
call lemonade over here.

16:32.866 --> 16:34.765
- Taino lemonade.
- Is it kid friendly?

16:34.767 --> 16:36.099
Oh yeah for sure. of course.

16:36.101 --> 16:38.168
- Alright, what time?
- Uh, Taino-thirty.

16:38.170 --> 16:40.674
- It's Taino time, bro.
- It's Taino time, baby.

16:41.674 --> 16:44.208
- I appreciate you.
- It was nice meeting you.

16:44.210 --> 16:47.078
- Good to meet y'all.
- We'll see you later, hopefully.

17:01.059 --> 17:01.861
No...

17:02.928 --> 17:05.031
Do you think he's here with us?

17:05.330 --> 17:06.832
Yeah I can feel it.

17:16.675 --> 17:18.308
Cool, a dolphin whisperer.

17:22.114 --> 17:23.682
Come on you can do it.

17:25.916 --> 17:26.917
Come on Luke!

18:16.266 --> 18:18.800
Come on man you
gonna know this by now.

18:18.802 --> 18:21.404
Didn't you get this in the class
we studied all weekend for this.

18:21.406 --> 18:23.004
Ten dollar lemonades!

18:23.006 --> 18:25.174
Hey, what's going on my
man!

18:25.176 --> 18:27.108
- How you doing man.
- How you all doing?

18:27.110 --> 18:28.210
How you guys doing?

18:28.212 --> 18:29.247
Everything good?

18:29.714 --> 18:30.882
- Welcome!
- Yeah man!

18:31.115 --> 18:32.916
- What's your name big man?
- Luke.

18:33.184 --> 18:34.853
- Luke.
- I'm Skylar.

18:35.086 --> 18:37.251
- Sky for the cool kids.
- Ooh man!

18:37.253 --> 18:38.254
Am I cool kid?

18:38.888 --> 18:39.890
Mmm, we'll see.

18:40.157 --> 18:41.258
Alright, alright.

18:42.493 --> 18:43.591
You gotta get some conch now,
you're on Taino Island man.

18:43.593 --> 18:45.860
- Oh yes!
- You gotta get some conch fritters

18:45.862 --> 18:48.032
- Conch salad, conch something.
- Conch taco.

18:48.331 --> 18:51.332
- We have everything but conch tacos.
- Nah man.

18:51.334 --> 18:53.269
Those aren't a thing even
though they should be.

18:53.936 --> 18:56.238
I, uh, moved here for my
master's

18:56.240 --> 18:58.072
and just been throwing conch
into

18:58.074 --> 19:00.407
every ramen recipe like
three times a day.

19:00.409 --> 19:03.444
- It's really gross.
- It's actually not it's amazing.

19:03.446 --> 19:04.915
Don't listen to her.

19:05.315 --> 19:07.013
So you guys are here for school.

19:07.015 --> 19:09.383
Yeah we're studying marine
biology.

19:09.385 --> 19:10.386
What is that?

19:10.820 --> 19:12.255
It's the study of sea animals.

19:12.789 --> 19:15.759
- Cool.
- What do you feed dolphins?

19:17.127 --> 19:20.094
Uh, we don't we let the dolphins
just

19:20.096 --> 19:21.865
chase little fish in the ocean.

19:22.232 --> 19:24.734
It's really important that we
don't feed the dolphins.

19:25.001 --> 19:27.868
They will grow to expect that
people need to feed them.

19:27.870 --> 19:30.371
And they need to depend on each
other

19:30.373 --> 19:31.842
to hunt as a pod.

19:33.175 --> 19:35.508
You hear that, and they're
dangerous.

19:35.510 --> 19:38.346
Nah man, they're the most
peaceful creatures in the sea.

19:38.348 --> 19:40.313
Nice, loving creatures man nah.

19:40.315 --> 19:43.454
- Humans are far worse.
- Oh in every way...

19:44.119 --> 19:45.818
humanly possible.

19:45.821 --> 19:47.723
What if one came here alone?

19:47.924 --> 19:52.161
- They rarely separate from the pod...
- Yeah it's not really common.

19:52.795 --> 19:54.997
Wait, what's going on? What's
happening?

19:56.866 --> 19:57.867
Let's say...

19:59.167 --> 20:01.868
We... might... know...

20:01.870 --> 20:02.872
someone...

20:03.838 --> 20:04.840
who...

20:05.907 --> 20:07.342
May have met a dolphin.

20:07.877 --> 20:09.145
By itself.

20:09.912 --> 20:11.380
A dolphin approached you guys?

20:11.579 --> 20:12.781
On Taino beach?

20:13.882 --> 20:14.883
Is that bad?

20:15.416 --> 20:16.418
He likes us.

20:17.152 --> 20:18.852
He must be separated.

20:18.854 --> 20:21.824
Sure you all didn't just see a
big ol' manatee or something?

20:22.057 --> 20:23.988
If you see it again can you let
us know.

20:23.990 --> 20:25.394
It might need our help.

20:26.127 --> 20:27.259
Actually...

20:27.261 --> 20:29.331
you can come with us tomorrow I
mean,

20:29.530 --> 20:30.899
he'll come around?

20:31.298 --> 20:32.299
Uh.

20:32.600 --> 20:33.834
We got class.

20:34.035 --> 20:36.139
I don't have class, so I'm game.

20:37.271 --> 20:38.238
Cool.

20:38.240 --> 20:40.840
- Hey guys!
- Hey Sunshine!

20:40.842 --> 20:41.910
Here try this.

20:43.111 --> 20:45.844
I still have no idea what conch
is, but here we go.

20:45.846 --> 20:47.848
Ah, there he goes.

20:48.382 --> 20:49.414
- How is it?
- Mmm.

20:49.416 --> 20:50.449
Right?

20:50.452 --> 20:51.453
Not bad.

20:51.885 --> 20:53.384
- I kinda like it.
- Taino Island man.

20:53.386 --> 20:55.153
Welcome to Taino beach.

20:55.155 --> 20:56.889
Your hair is so pretty.

20:56.891 --> 20:58.160
Ah, thank you.

20:58.526 --> 21:00.892
My mom taught me how
to do it as a kid.

21:00.894 --> 21:02.897
She did my hair all the time.

21:07.934 --> 21:09.503
- Excuse me guys.
- Is she OK?

21:27.922 --> 21:28.889
Hey water bug.

21:29.955 --> 21:31.457
Please go back inside.

21:37.063 --> 21:39.900
- What's wrong?
- I want mom to come back.

21:45.105 --> 21:46.105
I miss her too.

21:46.506 --> 21:47.975
She is here with us.

21:49.241 --> 21:51.311
I see her everyday when I look
at you.

21:53.113 --> 21:55.548
But mom never taught me to fish
tail.

21:58.050 --> 21:59.150
I'll tell you what,

21:59.152 --> 22:01.488
Why don't you let me learn how
to do the fish tail.

22:02.453 --> 22:05.124
I'll make the best looking
fish tail you've ever seen.

22:05.457 --> 22:06.926
It'll be a disaster.

22:08.093 --> 22:10.331
It'll be the best looking
disaster you've ever seen.

22:10.562 --> 22:12.365
Dad you're such a cheeseball.

22:12.631 --> 22:13.900
And proud of it.

22:14.499 --> 22:16.935
Come on, you know it'll look
good.

22:21.140 --> 22:23.008
You wanna go back and join
everyone?

22:23.241 --> 22:24.243
Yeah.

22:31.249 --> 22:32.251
Dom!

22:32.517 --> 22:33.518
Hey!

22:34.018 --> 22:35.020
Dom!

22:35.652 --> 22:37.022
Where this boy is?

22:37.456 --> 22:39.025
What is it Naz?

22:40.092 --> 22:41.992
How 'bout you and me work this
out man?

22:41.994 --> 22:43.360
What your problem is?

