can you do that?

30:37.624 --> 30:38.728
Which one of you?

30:39.193 --> 30:40.395
Yes I knew it.

30:40.694 --> 30:42.629
So..what I'm actually doing is

30:43.898 --> 30:44.999
calibrating this,

30:45.632 --> 30:47.769
gauge, because the last time I
dove,

30:48.002 --> 30:50.472
- I ran out of oxygen.
