30:50.705 --> 30:52.071
There we go. What up girls!

30:52.073 --> 30:53.641
- Hey!
- Hey guys!

30:54.475 --> 30:55.741
How was that dive?

30:55.743 --> 30:58.812
- It was alright.
- See anything interesting?

30:58.814 --> 31:00.447
- Same old, same old.
- Not really this time.

31:00.449 --> 31:01.679
What are you guys doing?

31:01.681 --> 31:03.782
I'm trying to make sure that I
don't

31:03.784 --> 31:06.118
explode, the next time I dive.

31:06.120 --> 31:09.391
How do you find a dolphin pod in
Taino island?

31:10.690 --> 31:11.793
Uhh, OK

31:12.460 --> 31:13.760
So...

31:13.762 --> 31:16.661
Taino is cool because it is
completely surrounded by coral.

31:16.663 --> 31:18.897
And it's why pirates actually
love this island

31:18.899 --> 31:21.533
Because there's a giant coral
reef

31:21.535 --> 31:23.071
