island.

31:23.470 --> 31:24.671
This. Taino island.

31:25.706 --> 31:26.708
And...

31:26.939 --> 31:28.476
Say this is the reef.

31:28.875 --> 31:31.676
Goes all around the island, all
zig zaggy.

31:31.678 --> 31:32.946
Except in two spots.

31:33.947 --> 31:35.080
So back in the day

