for the first time didn't know.

31:40.053 --> 31:41.890
And the ships would hit the
island and sink.

31:42.121 --> 31:43.987
That's why there's all this
buried treasure.

31:43.989 --> 31:45.525
All around here.

31:45.792 --> 31:47.257
So all of the dolphins are
swimming

31:47.259 --> 31:48.528
around here now.

31:49.729 --> 31:51.198
That probably got Echo, stuck
in the inside of the reef.

31:51.598 --> 31:53.598
Because you know it's low tide
during the day,

31:53.600 --> 31:54.698
And high tide during the night.

31:54.700 --> 31:56.869
And the dolphins feed
only in the day really.

31:56.871 --> 31:59.106
And so what probably
happened with our dolphin.

31:59.938 --> 32:00.972
Is,

32:00.974 --> 32:02.205
He got separated

32:02.207 --> 32:03.273
the tide rose

32:03.275 --> 32:04.841
