32:04.843 --> 32:06.010
And he couldn't escape

32:06.012 --> 32:08.212
so all of his friends, ditched
him.

32:08.214 --> 32:09.746
cause they're not good friends.

32:09.748 --> 32:11.117
Don't do that to your friends.

32:11.583 --> 32:13.719
What about echo location?

32:14.786 --> 32:16.553
Pods not even going to get close
enough

32:16.555 --> 32:17.922
so that they can hear each
other.

32:17.924 --> 32:20.624
- Yeah that's the thing.
- Yeah cause this is,

32:20.626 --> 32:21.992
the great wall of China.

32:21.994 --> 32:24.595
Two openings.
We have another opening on the south west

32:24.597 --> 32:26.030
part, that's where all the
fishermen

32:26.032 --> 32:28.564
go out, and yeah majority of
them live there too.

32:28.566 --> 32:31.201
And, so we gonna have to try and
focus,

32:31.203 --> 32:33.102
- get something to focus them to come in.
- Got it yeah.

32:33.104 --> 32:34.871
Cause they're
feeding, they already have

32:34.873 --> 32:35.872
enough fish on the
outside of the reef.

32:35.874 --> 32:37.139
We could do that we can think
of something.

32:37.142 --> 32:38.274
So we just need to find

32:38.276 --> 32:40.042
