32:40.044 --> 32:41.645
Exactly other than fish.

32:41.647 --> 32:43.850
Looks like we
found our porpoise.

32:44.248 --> 32:47.152
Oh my god, I love that so much.

32:49.154 --> 32:51.491
Keep it up, I love the dad
jokes.

