there's no guarantee that the
corrosion

40:04.713 --> 40:07.314
hasn't just destroyed all of the
parts

40:07.316 --> 40:08.249
anyways.

40:08.251 --> 40:10.084
It'll take forever
just to put them back

40:10.086 --> 40:11.489
together and see
if they even work.

40:12.620 --> 40:14.655
We have to at least try I
mean...

40:14.657 --> 40:17.093
