40:26.135 --> 40:28.237
You guys don't know
Simmons this dude was...

40:28.738 --> 40:29.940
bananas.

40:30.305 --> 40:31.671
There's no telling if this

40:31.673 --> 40:33.309
is even remotely possible.

40:34.074 --> 40:35.076
I scuba.

40:37.344 --> 40:39.114
You have your divers cert?

40:39.314 --> 40:40.316
Oh yeah.

40:40.748 --> 40:42.249
Spring break, Caba.

40:44.185 --> 40:45.588
Didn't we all?

40:50.759 --> 40:52.360
You know my wife used to say,

40:52.627 --> 40:54.293
you can sit around your whole
life

40:54.295 --> 40:55.697
with just your toes in the water

40:56.563 --> 40:58.000
or you can dive in.

41:04.806 --> 41:06.141
I say let's do it.

41:07.375 --> 41:08.507
I'm in.

41:08.509 --> 41:09.511
Me too.

41:10.677 --> 41:12.080
You got me, I'm in.

41:13.047 --> 41:14.079
Alright.

41:14.081 --> 41:15.083
- Let's get it!
- Great!

41:15.649 --> 41:16.681
6 AM tomorrow?

41:16.683 --> 41:17.749
Ooh.

41:19.721 --> 41:20.723
Yup.

41:22.655 --> 41:23.657
Alright.

41:27.462 --> 41:28.464
Is that good?

41:28.662 --> 41:29.694
Little tight.

41:29.696 --> 41:31.364
Well, stop skipping leg day.

41:31.366 --> 41:33.369
There is no such thing as leg
day.

41:35.135 --> 41:36.205
Rule number one,

41:37.205 --> 41:38.305
steady breathing.

41:40.173 --> 41:42.140
If he stays with me he'll
survive.

41:42.142 --> 41:43.379
Can I get that in writing.

41:46.280 --> 41:47.647
This is the place guys.

41:48.615 --> 41:49.446
Hey sweetie,

41:49.448 --> 41:51.348
if you see any fishing boats out
here

41:51.350 --> 41:52.584
you blow the horn.

41:52.587 --> 41:54.455
I can hear it underwater I'll be
right up.

41:54.655 --> 41:55.656
My hero.

41:56.990 --> 41:59.723
Uh, remember you gotta
take a big step out frontwards.

41:59.725 --> 42:00.758
Frontwards.

42:00.760 --> 42:02.428
Clint, turn around dude.

42:45.704 --> 42:48.271
Chop. Chop. Chopped and screwed.

42:48.273 --> 42:50.576
Chop. Chop. Chopped and screwed.

42:50.775 --> 42:53.079
Chop. Chop. Chopped and screwed.

42:53.377 --> 42:55.548
Disappoint my father.

43:03.156 --> 43:05.154
Luke look there he is!

43:05.157 --> 43:06.257
Hey Echo!

43:06.259 --> 43:07.756
Oh no you got another one.

43:07.758 --> 43:09.692
Echo stop with the buoys!

43:09.694 --> 43:11.195
Those aren't yours!

43:11.197 --> 43:13.229
No more fetch crazy people are
trying

43:13.231 --> 43:14.634
to kill you for this stuff.

44:16.726 --> 44:18.795
Guys! Guys! Echo can hear this!

44:19.563 --> 44:21.833
Echo can hear this under the
water!

44:30.907 --> 44:31.909
Boss!

44:34.545 --> 44:35.743
Boss!

44:35.745 --> 44:37.278
Look what they doing!

44:37.280 --> 44:38.846
Man it looks like you got a
problem there!

44:38.848 --> 44:41.349
Boss I need some money so I can
put fuel in

44:41.351 --> 44:43.586
