44:55.964 --> 44:59.602
You're the tenth one here
today looking for charity.

45:39.941 --> 45:43.309
Baby girl,
I love you more than diamonds and pearls.

45:43.311 --> 45:46.615
- Babes thats you?
- Just what my weary eyes needed.

45:47.316 --> 45:49.548
Only girl more beautiful than
the island itself.

45:49.550 --> 45:51.253
- See my baby.
- And you,

45:51.653 --> 45:54.320
The only fishermen she'd ever
let kiss her.

45:56.458 --> 45:57.956
- Mm mmm, what you say baby?
- Everything's good.

45:57.958 --> 45:58.791
Feeling any better?

45:58.793 --> 46:00.894
Everything's good baby, you
alright?

46:00.896 --> 46:02.828
- Where I belong now.
- Good.

46:02.831 --> 46:05.096
Hey Moe! You been keeping my
boy safe today!

46:05.098 --> 46:06.865
Well you see we
back in one piece right?

46:06.867 --> 46:08.036
All I can ask for.

46:08.869 --> 46:10.271
- OK.
- Hey!

46:11.473 --> 46:13.342
- What's on your mind.
- I was at the market earlier.

46:14.040 --> 46:16.477
- I overheard some of the other guys talking.
- Yeah?

46:16.778 --> 46:17.780
'Bout what?

46:18.880 --> 46:20.882
