01:01:28.536 --> 01:01:29.868
We only have two days left.

01:01:29.870 --> 01:01:32.306
Okay, so what do we do?

01:01:35.409 --> 01:01:36.812
I know where we can get some
metal.

01:01:37.478 --> 01:01:39.448
